title: Blac Chyna Steps Out in Red Latex Catsuit as She Nears Post-Baby Goal Weight
text: Blac Chyna Steps Out in Red Latex Catsuit as She Nears Post-Baby Goal Weight by Jackie Willis 5:30 AM PST, February 23, 2017 Photo: Instagram Meow! Blac Chyna most certainly turned heads when she hit the town in a skintight catsuit and matching corset on Wednesday. After revealing to her social media followers that she's lost 40 pounds since giving birth to daughter Dream in November, the 28-year-old reality star stepped out in the curve-hugging red number and high-heeled ankle boots for a girls night with pal Amber Rose. The duo posed for a number of selfies together on Snapchat that featured their sexy styles. On Tuesday night, Chyna also shared on Snapchat that she'd gone from weighing 192 to 152.4 pounds, adding that she's working towards a goal weight of 130 pounds by this summer. Photo: Instagram A post shared by The Kardashians ☘️ (@blacchynarmy) on Feb 22, 2017 at 9:38pm PST A post shared by The Kardashians ☘️ (@blacchynarmy) on Feb 22, 2017 at 10:21pm PST Prior to slipping into her catsuit, Rob Kardashian's on-again, off-again fiancee posted some nude photos of herself in bed to Instagram, flaunting her impressive weight loss.
